UCM - What it will have

UCM will be nothing like B-Card. It will have many unrivalled features
never before seen in B-Card. These include

    16 Colour Cards
   
    Multi Language Functionality

    All objects movable

    All objects erasable

    500 level undo feature

    Text in any font, and size

And there will be more! If you would like to be sent the latest details
of UCM, then send an Email to:

trogladite@trogsoft.freeserve.co.uk
putting "UCM Details" in the subject line or you won't get a reply since
the whole UCM details distribution is automated by my Email program.

